  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><strong>Tuesday 8th March 2016, Godalming</strong>- Inghams are expanding their already popular Swiss short breaks to include selected chalets and Chalet Hotels in <a data-udi="umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb}" title="Austria">Austria</a> (<a data-udi="umb://document/415e45d2352b4e61b39f1f3f2a9ec53d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/415e45d2352b4e61b39f1f3f2a9ec53d}" title="St Christoph">St. Christoph</a>) and <a data-udi="umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5}" title="France">France</a> (<a data-udi="umb://document/1424e5dc124549bebe48ab72e02ec9cb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1424e5dc124549bebe48ab72e02ec9cb}" title="Les Arcs">Les Arcs</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565" href="/{localLink:umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565}" title="Tignes">Tignes</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/50690c0f70c74050930d18799cab6fa8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/50690c0f70c74050930d18799cab6fa8}" title="Val Thorens">Val Thorens</a>) on 9th April 2016 departures. Return flights are available from Manchester, Edinburgh and London Gatwick airports. So a short burst of spring skiing in some of Europe’s highest and most snow sure resort just got that little bit easier!</p>
<p><strong>Here are our New Short Break packages</strong><br /><strong>Tignes</strong>, France- A high resort in the extensive Espace Killy ski area, Tignes is a great choice for late season spring skiing. Even better from 9th-16th April Tignes is home to the Francofolies Music festival which fills an already vibrant Tignes with music! Inghams is offering 4 nights chalet catering at the 3.5 diamond <a data-udi="umb://document/e9d2ebb7a6e14f1c82fecf5bf3cc63af" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e9d2ebb7a6e14f1c82fecf5bf3cc63af}" title="Xtra Chalet Le Curling">Chalet Hotel Le Curling</a>, Tignes, France from £439 per person departing 9th April 2016. Price includes return flights from London Gatwick to Geneva and resort transfers. For more information or to book visit <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk">www.inghams.co.uk</a> or call 01483 791 114.</p>
<p><strong>Val Thorens</strong>, France- As Europe’s highest resort and part of the Three Valleys Ski Area Val Thorens is a fantastic choice for a short spring ski break! Inghams is offering 4 nights chalet catering at the 3.5 diamond at <a data-udi="umb://document/d73759b2f0e54404ba37088ebf6495bd" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d73759b2f0e54404ba37088ebf6495bd}" title="Chalet Maryse">Chalet Maryse,</a> Val Thorens France from £469 per person departing 9th April 2016. Price includes return flights from London Gatwick to Geneva and resort transfers. For more information or to book visit <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk">www.inghams.co.uk</a> or call 01483 791 114.</p>
<p><strong>Les Arcs,</strong> France- Enjoy two weeks of activities, concerts and games in Les Arcs during Spring Final when the resort comes to life with entertainment. Inghams is offering 4 nights, chalet catering at the 4 diamond <a data-udi="umb://document/208e630b396d4ed18cc77030b8f9dffa" href="/{localLink:umb://document/208e630b396d4ed18cc77030b8f9dffa}" title="Chalet Spitzberg">Chalet Spitzberg</a>, Les Arcs, France from £439 per person departing 9th April 2016. Price includes return flights from London Gatwick to Geneva and resort transfers. For more information or to book visit <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk">www.inghams .co.uk</a> or call 01483 791 114.</p>
<p><strong>St. Christoph, Austria-</strong> Enjoy a few days in Inghams’ ski-in/ ski-out Chalet Hotel in the heart of the Arlberg ski area. Inghams is offering 4 nights chalet catering at the 4.5 diamond <a data-udi="umb://document/415e45d2352b4e61b39f1f3f2a9ec53d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/415e45d2352b4e61b39f1f3f2a9ec53d}" title="St Christoph">Chalet Hotel St. Christoph</a>, Austria from £469 per person departing 9th April 2016. Price includes return flights from London Gatwick to Innsbruck and resort transfers. For more information or to book visit www.inghams .co.uk or call 01483 791 114.</p>
<p>For more information about our short breaks visit <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/skishortbreaks">www.inghams.co.uk/skishortbreaks</a> or call 01483 791 114.</p>
